  "detailed_description": "Benvenuti a Roma Join Kate Robinson and her daughter Nicole in <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >First Time in Rome</h2>, the exhilarating sequel to the First Time hidden-object adventure series. Join them as they discover Eternal City's rich history, seeing stunning ruins, vibrant marketplaces, and captivating neighborhoods..<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948780/extras/3fab73fd90b14c1929e9c1b1ff19ddfd.poster.avif?t=1729487972\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948780/extras/3fab73fd90b14c1929e9c1b1ff19ddfd.webm?t=1729487972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948780/extras/3fab73fd90b14c1929e9c1b1ff19ddfd.mp4?t=1729487972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This time, the mother-daughter duo go on a trip through Rome, uncovering secrets of the past while strolling along ancient streets and experiencing the vibrant culture of modern Italy. Play over 30 captivating minigames, from solving historical mysteries to discovering hidden treasures in bustling markets. Every corner of Rome offers a new challenge and a glimpse into its rich heritage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948780/extras/3d36e7b094896c47b13b8e7aba3fe11c.poster.avif?t=1729487972\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948780/extras/3d36e7b094896c47b13b8e7aba3fe11c.webm?t=1729487972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948780/extras/3d36e7b094896c47b13b8e7aba3fe11c.mp4?t=1729487972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore Rome through different levels<br></li><li>Enjoy over 30 engaging minigames inspired by Rome<br></li><li>Revisit locations in Unlimited Mode<br></li><li>Unlock achievements as you play<br></li><li>Download exclusive wallpapers and the full soundtrack</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948780/extras/741ce76ba40862f6d75f6216de36e79d.poster.avif?t=1729487972\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948780/extras/741ce76ba40862f6d75f6216de36e79d.webm?t=1729487972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948780/extras/741ce76ba40862f6d75f6216de36e79d.mp4?t=1729487972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Step into the charm and allure of Rome with Kate and Nicole. Uncover the stories and secrets that make this city eternal. Benvenuti nella Città Eterna!",
